data.description: NEW PRICE .... Charming manufactured home in a Gated Community 55+ nestle against the backdrop of a golf course. This cozy home boasts a 2- car carport, a petite utility room and a spacious living area. Featuring 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, it offers a serene retreat surrounded by mature trees. Located in a vibrant community with plethora of activities, this is a delightful haven for those seeking comfort and leisure. This centrally-located home is close to shopping, restaurants and major highways. Located in Orange Blossom Gardens, close to the Villages Spanish Springs town square with nightly entertainment, restaurants, shopping and medical facilities. A golf course community with lots and lots of activities besides golf, including swimming pool, tennis, pickle ball, soft ball and many community activity clubs. Easy to show
